5️⃣ 1LOD – COI Offline Upload

✅ Use Case Name

1LOD View – Offline Endorsement Document Upload (COI)

⸻

✅ Description

PM / 1LOD users should be able to upload offline endorsement documents for COI and confirm endorsement status.

⸻

✅ System Behavior

🔹 Navigation & Visibility
	•	Stage 3 view for 1LOD / PM
	•	Stage 3a visible to RFO
	•	Stage 3b visible to PM / 1LOD
	•	UI displays stage as “3”

⸻

🔹 Document Upload
	•	Upload option available on screen
	•	File browser supports local selection
	•	Supported formats: PDF, DOC, DOCX, JPG, PNG
	•	File size limit: 10MB per file
	•	Multiple file upload supported

⸻

🔹 Offline Confirmation
	•	“Yes – Endorsed as Offline” option available
	•	Confirmation status displayed
	•	User ID captured

⸻

🔹 Validation
	•	File format and size validation enforced
	•	Required fields must be completed
	•	At least one document upload required (if applicable)

⸻

🔹 Progress Tracking
	•	Visual progress indicator displayed
	•	Completed steps marked
	•	Remaining steps visible

⸻

🔹 Audit
	•	Document upload details logged
	•	Endorsement confirmation recorded
	•	Timestamp and user captured

⸻

✅ Target Output

PM / 1LOD is able to:
	•	Upload documents
	•	Confirm endorsement
	•	Complete submission

System should:
	•	Validate inputs
	•	Display status
	•	Log all actions

⸻

